Additional seat controller
Conveniently located inside the cocoon for easy reach when
reclined. This control will only operate to a certain point, the main
seat controller will need to be used to return seat to the fully
upright position.

Welcome to the Qantas Skybed.
Whether you are relaxing, working, being entertained or sleeping, your
comfort is our priority. With extensive seat adjustments and an inbuilt back
massager, the Qantas Skybed offers outstanding comfort in every position,
while the unique cocoon-style design provides new levels of privacy.
